Packages
analysis analysis package: a package implementing parallel algorithms for numerical differentiation and integration, and also including more complex transformations such as convolution.
graph graph package: a collection of classes for representing graphs, hyper-graphs and algorithms operating on such discrete finite structures.
graph.coarsening package defines abstract classes and implements algorithms for coarsening graphs.
graph.packing Optimization package that obtains near-optimal solution to the 1- and 2-packing combinatorial optimization problem.
graph.partitioning Package defines interfaces and implements algorithms for graph and hyper-graph partitioning.
parallel parallel package: an implementation of all the synchronization, communication & coordination primitives required in popt4jlib.
parallel.distributed Extends the basic functionality found in the parallel package over many remote JVMs distributed over a network of machines.
popt4jlib popt4jlib: a parallel optimization library for Java.
popt4jlib.DE Differential Evolution Algorithms Parallel Implementation.
popt4jlib.EA Evolutionary Algorithms Parallel Implementation Package Specification hyperlink Related Documentation hyperlink
popt4jlib.GA Genetic Algorithms Parallel Implementation.
popt4jlib.GradientDescent Gradient-Descent Type Algorithms Parallel Implementation (suitable for real vector function optimization).
popt4jlib.LocalSearch Local Search algorithms parallel implementation for combinatorial optimization problems.
popt4jlib.MonteCarlo Monte-Carlo Search Parallel Implementation (aka random search) Package Specification hyperlink Related Documentation hyperlink
popt4jlib.MSSC Package implements algorithms for Minimum-Sum-of-Square(-Errors)-Clustering, a well-defined optimization problem.
popt4jlib.MSSC1D Package implements a Parallel Dynamic-Programming (DP) - based algorithm for clustering in a Minimum-Sum-of-Square-Error-Distances a sequence of numbers.
popt4jlib.NumberPartitioning Package defines parallel/distributed versions of well-known Number Partitioning algorithms.
popt4jlib.PS Particle Swarm Optimization Algorithms Parallel Implementation.
popt4jlib.SA Simulated Annealing Algorithms Parallel Implementation.
tests tests package: defines functions used for testing the optimization algorithms in the popt4jlib library.
utils utils package: containing useful classes and methods including I/O manipulation.
